1
00:00:29,345 --> 00:00:38,273
Today we are celebrating Sahastrara day.

2
00:00:38,833 --> 00:00:48,877
Perhaps we have not realised what a day it must have been.

3
00:00:50,680 --> 00:00:58,731
Without opening the Sahastrara, God Itself was a myth,

4
00:00:59,293 --> 00:01:07,136
religion itself was a myth, and all talk about Divinity was a myth.

5
00:01:08,112 --> 00:01:12,989
People believed in it but it was just a belief.

6
00:01:13,489 --> 00:01:19,749
And the science, as it was put forward,

7
00:01:20,152 --> 00:01:38,759
was about to obliterate all the value system,
all the proof of God Almighty.

8
00:01:39,802 --> 00:01:45,393
If you see in the history, one after another,

9
00:01:45,582 --> 00:01:50,464
when science established itself,

10
00:01:50,895 --> 00:01:58,223
the people who are so-called in charge of
the helm of affairs in religion,

11
00:01:58,490 --> 00:02:05,629
in different religions tried to cope with the findings of science.

12
00:02:05,894 --> 00:02:15,179
They tried to show that:
“All right, if it is said this much – is in the Bible,

13
00:02:15,369 --> 00:02:23,323
and if it is wrong we should correct it.”
Especially Augustine did that.

14
00:02:23,724 --> 00:02:30,957
And it started looking as if it’s all a stupidity this,

15
00:02:32,053 --> 00:02:35,638
these scriptures were just mythical.

16
00:02:35,753 --> 00:02:43,220
At least the Koran itself, though, had lots of things which were

17
00:02:43,711 --> 00:02:49,886
describing the biology of today.

18
00:02:51,630 --> 00:02:59,061
They could not believe that human beings
were specially created by God.

19
00:02:59,186 --> 00:03:03,845
They thought it was a matter of chance that one after another

20
00:03:03,944 --> 00:03:10,206
the animals acquired a situation by which they became human beings.

21
00:03:13,967 --> 00:03:19,416
Thus all the time Divinity was challenged

22
00:03:19,664 --> 00:03:24,371
and there was no way of giving a proof of whatever

23
00:03:24,512 --> 00:03:31,396
is said in the Bible or in the Koran or in the Gita

24
00:03:31,567 --> 00:03:35,258
or in the Upanishadas or in the Torah.

25
00:03:35,315 --> 00:03:39,207
Any one of these things could not be proved

26
00:03:39,464 --> 00:03:42,942
because it was still just a faith.

27
00:03:43,132 --> 00:03:46,339
Very, very few people got their Realisation

28
00:03:46,448 --> 00:03:49,209
and when they talked,  people did not believe them

29
00:03:49,234 --> 00:03:53,249
and thought that they are just trying to say something

30
00:03:53,274 --> 00:03:59,713
which they are using to propound their own theories.

31
00:03:59,860 --> 00:04:07,211
So the whole thing became a kind of dead science.

32
00:04:07,376 --> 00:04:13,397
There was no science of religion.

33
00:04:13,426 --> 00:04:18,425
People started thinking that:
what’s the use of following these ten commandments

34
00:04:18,656 --> 00:04:26,335
or these strict rules of life,
because by following that you gain nothing.

35
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:29,041
You lose all the fun of the life.

36
00:04:29,089 --> 00:04:33,578
And why think of gaining some punyas also.

37
00:04:33,603 --> 00:04:42,624
And that is how all the time there was
a big derailment of human value system.

38
00:04:43,106 --> 00:04:51,408
Also these organised religions, this monolithic organised religions

39
00:04:51,508 --> 00:04:59,118
started taking to [a] course of gaining power, or gaining money,

40
00:04:59,118 --> 00:05:03,252
because they thought that’s the only way
you can control people and can go on.

41
00:05:03,334 --> 00:05:10,354
They were least bothered as to deliver the goods,
whatever have been described in the Bible.

42
00:05:10,455 --> 00:05:17,547
Bible of course was tampered [with] very much
and has been lot of changes in that.

43
00:05:17,663 --> 00:05:24,465
And a person like Paul, and Peter, who joined together,

44
00:05:24,629 --> 00:05:28,112
tried to spoil most of the Truth.

45
00:05:28,575 --> 00:05:31,486
Though Koran was not so much touched

46
00:05:31,595 --> 00:05:35,184
but still is dealt with more the right side,

47
00:05:35,276 --> 00:05:39,473
with the reproductive system and all those things.

48
00:05:39,574 --> 00:05:43,127
And so many things are still ambiguous.

49
00:05:43,969 --> 00:05:49,563
Now simultaneously two things have happened,
I don’t know if you are aware of it or not.

50
00:05:49,641 --> 00:05:53,932
First thing that has happened is that now we have

51
00:05:53,994 --> 00:05:57,614
a new science of microbiology

52
00:05:57,854 --> 00:06:05,945
in which we have discovered that every cell has got a DNA tape.

53
00:06:06,352 --> 00:06:10,938
Every cell has got a program in it.

54
00:06:10,967 --> 00:06:16,944
As we have in a computer a chip, every cell has got

55
00:06:17,227 --> 00:06:24,245
a tape in it, in a way, that it is programmed.

56
00:06:24,542 --> 00:06:28,383
And according to that program a development takes place.

57
00:06:28,408 --> 00:06:31,213
Now imagine the intricacy of the whole thing!

58
00:06:31,379 --> 00:06:35,077
So many computers are already programmed

59
00:06:35,207 --> 00:06:39,708
and all these cells have these in them.

60
00:06:39,842 --> 00:06:47,376
So a very mysterious sort of a thing
has come up

61
00:06:47,401 --> 00:06:50,798
before the scientists and they cannot explain it.

62
00:06:50,896 --> 00:06:55,975
They cannot explain many things but one of them is this.

63
00:06:56,087 --> 00:06:59,372
Now what Sahaja Yoga has done is that

64
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:03,879
it has proved that it is the Will of God,

65
00:07:04,020 --> 00:07:07,758
it is the desire of God, the Will of God,

66
00:07:07,837 --> 00:07:13,302
which is doing all the work.

67
00:07:13,818 --> 00:07:15,597
And it has been proved.

68
00:07:15,711 --> 00:07:21,273
All these Chaitanya, Adi Shakti, is nothing but the Will of God.

69
00:07:21,552 --> 00:07:24,759
And Will of God is the One

70
00:07:24,915 --> 00:07:28,433
is working out everything very harmoniously.

71
00:07:28,527 --> 00:07:31,698
I don’t know if some of you must have read my book,

72
00:07:31,723 --> 00:07:36,564
first book, where I have described how this Earth was created.

73
00:07:36,738 --> 00:07:40,832
There was a bang, but it was very harmonious,

74
00:07:40,906 --> 00:07:47,810
and how it developed is through the Will of God.

75
00:07:49,024 --> 00:07:56,293
So everything was done in a way that God’s will was working it out.

76
00:07:57,306 --> 00:08:01,694
Now the Will of God you are feeling it, on your finger tips.

77
00:08:01,952 --> 00:08:07,642
After Realisation, now, you have discovered the the absolute science,

78
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:13,406
which is the Will of God, which is an absolute science.

79
00:08:13,557 --> 00:08:17,622
You people know that we have cured people through Sahaja Yoga.

80
00:08:17,646 --> 00:08:21,553
You also know giving bandhan, and all that, things work out.

81
00:08:21,605 --> 00:08:24,260
So many things work out automatically

82
00:08:24,284 --> 00:08:27,770
after Realisation that people don’t want to believe.

83
00:08:27,876 --> 00:08:30,128
In the beginning people would not believe

84
00:08:30,164 --> 00:08:34,352
when the scientists told them something, but now it is, you can see,

85
00:08:34,377 --> 00:08:37,730
the science is always in the flux, all the time changing.

86
00:08:37,931 --> 00:08:40,000
One theory is again challenged.

87
00:08:40,024 --> 00:08:41,951
Another theory’s again challenged.

88
00:08:42,012 --> 00:08:48,945
But Sahaja Yoga has exposed you to that Great Truth of science

89
00:08:49,050 --> 00:08:54,727
which cannot be challenged, which is all there.

90
00:08:54,915 --> 00:09:01,309
So anybody who comes out with any new proposal

91
00:09:01,518 --> 00:09:07,303
about defaming God, or saying that there is no God,

92
00:09:07,325 --> 00:09:10,052
we can prove, not [only] that there is God,

93
00:09:10,076 --> 00:09:12,224
but that everything, the creation of this Earth,

94
00:09:12,247 --> 00:09:15,577
the creation of human beings and everything was done

95
00:09:15,650 --> 00:09:21,046
harmoniously by the Will of God.

96
00:09:21,410 --> 00:09:24,482
If Will of God has done everything,

97
00:09:24,506 --> 00:09:27,117
the human beings should not take any credit

98
00:09:27,181 --> 00:09:30,354
for discovering some things which were created by God.

99
00:09:30,380 --> 00:09:33,120
Supposing this carpet is made by somebody

100
00:09:33,176 --> 00:09:36,480
and we start discovering all the colours, what is so great?

101
00:09:36,513 --> 00:09:39,600
It is all there. You cannot create.

102
00:09:39,912 --> 00:09:44,094
So it is not the creation part of it [which is] so much important

103
00:09:44,222 --> 00:09:50,994
but the fashioning of this world, whole thing
was done by the Will of God.

104
00:09:51,683 --> 00:09:57,925
Now if the Will of God is so important,  it has to be proved.

105
00:09:58,977 --> 00:10:03,723
And now through Sahaja Yoga, after the breaking of the Sahastrara,

106
00:10:03,977 --> 00:10:09,896
you have now, for the first time, felt the Will of God,

107
00:10:10,626 --> 00:10:12,660
which is such an important thing,

108
00:10:12,685 --> 00:10:16,510
but for us it is come to us so Sahaj that we don’t understand.

109
00:10:16,537 --> 00:10:20,289
We just give the bandhan and the things work out and

110
00:10:20,348 --> 00:10:25,916
we feel that the things have worked out,

111
00:10:25,940 --> 00:10:30,129
so it is bandhan which has worked out, and

112
00:10:33,896 --> 00:10:37,213
we have managed everything. It’s not so.

113
00:10:37,355 --> 00:10:39,332
It’s much more than that.

114
00:10:39,418 --> 00:10:47,899
We have now become part
and parcel of that Big Computer of that Will of God.

115
00:10:47,928 --> 00:10:56,282
We have become the medium,
or we can say the channels, of that Will of God.

116
00:10:56,344 --> 00:11:03,039
We are connected with that Will of God
which created all this Universe.

117
00:11:03,039 --> 00:11:08,143
So everything we can manage

118
00:11:08,272 --> 00:11:14,338
because we have got the Absolute Science in our hand.

119
00:11:14,666 --> 00:11:21,792
The Absolute Science which will work out
the betterment of the whole world.

120
00:11:22,068 --> 00:11:27,370
We can prove it to the scientist that there is a Will of God

121
00:11:27,397 --> 00:11:30,536
which has done all this creation.

122
00:11:30,630 --> 00:11:35,498
Even evolutionary process is the Will of God.

123
00:11:35,863 --> 00:11:40,612
Without His Will nothing could have happened.

124
00:11:40,612 --> 00:11:48,670
So many people used to say that – not even a blade of grass
moves without the Will of God.

125
00:11:48,834 --> 00:11:51,165
Which is a very true thing.

126
00:11:51,728 --> 00:12:00,567
And you have seen now that –
the Will of God we have got as our own power.

127
00:12:01,228 --> 00:12:06,264
We can use it. So how important it is to be a sahaja yogi.

128
00:12:06,289 --> 00:12:11,126
Perhaps we don’t realise how important it is to be a sahaja yogi.

129
00:12:11,150 --> 00:12:16,138
Sahaja Yoga is not only for saying “Mother, I am full of joy,

130
00:12:16,215 --> 00:12:19,745
I am enjoying myself. I got purified.

131
00:12:19,769 --> 00:12:22,894
Everything is fine“. But for what?

132
00:12:23,010 --> 00:12:25,442
Why did you get all these blessings?

133
00:12:25,466 --> 00:12:31,531
Why you have been cleansed?
So that this knowledge of the Will of God should be apparent in you.

134
00:12:31,556 --> 00:12:34,988
Not only that – should be a part and parcel of you.

135
00:12:35,199 --> 00:12:39,241
So we have to raise our level, we have to come up.

136
00:12:39,296 --> 00:12:44,302
For mediocre and ordinary people
it is really useless to give them Sahaja Yoga

137
00:12:44,327 --> 00:12:46,421
because they are good for nothing.

138
00:12:46,571 --> 00:12:49,550
They are not going to help us in any way

139
00:12:49,608 --> 00:12:53,812
because what is needed is now, today that,

140
00:12:53,838 --> 00:12:59,700
we should have people who can really manifest
and reflect the Will of God.

141
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:03,673
And for that, you can understand, we have to have very strong people

142
00:13:03,698 --> 00:13:08,802
because this Will has created the whole Universe, the Cosmos,

143
00:13:08,827 --> 00:13:15,318
this Mother Earth. Everything is created by this Will of God.

144
00:13:15,411 --> 00:13:22,375
So now we are exposed to a new dimension

145
00:13:22,469 --> 00:13:27,260
and that dimension is that we are the ones

146
00:13:27,326 --> 00:13:32,276
who are channels of that Will of God.

147
00:13:32,671 --> 00:13:40,850
So then what is our duty and what should we do about it?

148
00:13:41,253 --> 00:13:45,389
As a result of Sahastrara being opened out,

149
00:13:45,469 --> 00:13:48,593
one thing: the illusions have vanished.

150
00:13:50,545 --> 00:13:52,666
What you call [in] Sanskrit is bhranti.

151
00:13:52,997 --> 00:13:54,483
Illusions have vanished.

152
00:13:54,528 --> 00:14:05,701
You should have no illusion as to the existence of God Almighty,

153
00:14:06,741 --> 00:14:18,467
the power of his Will and the truth about Sahaja Yoga.

154
00:14:20,045 --> 00:14:25,406
You should have no doubts at all,
minimum of minimum should be like that.

155
00:14:25,611 --> 00:14:30,097
But while using this Power you should be aware

156
00:14:30,274 --> 00:14:39,976
that this Power is given to you
because you are capable of handling it.

157
00:14:41,026 --> 00:14:44,207
This is the Highest Power you could think of.

158
00:14:44,387 --> 00:14:51,659
Take any governor, take any minister,
anyone, they can be removed tomorrow.

159
00:14:51,887 --> 00:14:54,297
They can become corrupt.

160
00:14:54,338 --> 00:15:02,652
They can become absolutely devoid of
any knowledge of their own powers.

161
00:15:02,808 --> 00:15:07,487
There are many people who just get elected
without knowing what they have to do.

162
00:15:07,661 --> 00:15:10,849
So this is not just a conversion of people,

163
00:15:11,040 --> 00:15:13,823
it’s not only even transformation,

164
00:15:14,066 --> 00:15:18,114
but it is a new fashioning of a new human being

165
00:15:18,263 --> 00:15:27,201
which has come forward and which is capable
of carrying the Will of God further.

166
00:15:40,469 --> 00:15:44,936
So as a result of your Realisation, what you have got?

167
00:15:46,779 --> 00:15:52,055
The first thing that has happened is that your illusions have gone.

168
00:15:52,941 --> 00:15:58,264
You should have no illusions about God Almighty, His Will

169
00:15:58,327 --> 00:16:07,970
and that He is omnipotent, omnipresent and omniscient.

170
00:16:09,304 --> 00:16:14,425
All His omnipotence has done this work,

171
00:16:14,559 --> 00:16:18,234
and as a collective consciousness  you should also know that

172
00:16:18,250 --> 00:16:24,516
you are also omnipotent, omnipresent and omniscient.

173
00:16:25,085 --> 00:16:29,805
Omniscient is the thing, that He sees everything, knows everything.

174
00:16:30,217 --> 00:16:34,509
Part of it, that Power, is also within you.

175
00:16:34,937 --> 00:16:41,672
So to prove His omnipresence you have to all the time be aware

176
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:46,112
that you are sahaja yogis. When I find, even now,

177
00:16:46,957 --> 00:16:50,093
sahaja yogis struggling about their wives, their children,

178
00:16:50,115 --> 00:16:52,251
their house, their jobs,

179
00:16:52,307 --> 00:16:54,887
I start wondering what is their level now?

180
00:16:54,909 --> 00:17:02,870
Where are they?
When are they going to take up the role of what they have got?

181
00:17:03,138 --> 00:17:08,759
So the Omnipotent God who is everywhere,

182
00:17:09,030 --> 00:17:15,012
who has done all this, the Will of God that has worked it out,

183
00:17:15,259 --> 00:17:19,003
has to work through you people and you have to be

184
00:17:19,025 --> 00:17:25,856
very strong, very sensible, very wise, also very effective people.

185
00:17:26,886 --> 00:17:30,878
The more effective you become the more energy you will get.

186
00:17:31,009 --> 00:17:35,546
But still I feel that the sahaja yogis are more,

187
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:38,738
not taking the responsibility of understanding

188
00:17:38,818 --> 00:17:42,160
that they have to represent this God Almighty

189
00:17:42,225 --> 00:17:48,326
who is omnipresent, omniscient,

190
00:17:49,107 --> 00:17:53,279
who knows everything, who sees everything

191
00:17:53,306 --> 00:17:58,477
and who is potent, means Almighty.

192
00:18:01,230 --> 00:18:07,014
If you understand that this is what has happened
after opening the Sahastrara,

193
00:18:07,038 --> 00:18:13,748
that you have now got the power
which has these three qualities in it.

194
00:18:13,773 --> 00:18:20,843
Say now this big thing has to be supported by a strong pillars,

195
00:18:20,999 --> 00:18:24,693
but supposing if they are not strong, it will fall down.

196
00:18:24,832 --> 00:18:28,719
In the same way such a Great Power which has come to you.

197
00:18:28,745 --> 00:18:31,476
For that we don’t need very successful people,

198
00:18:31,525 --> 00:18:34,404
we don’t need people who have a big name

199
00:18:34,430 --> 00:18:36,288
or those who have lots of money,

200
00:18:36,337 --> 00:18:38,658
what we need [is] people of character,

201
00:18:38,755 --> 00:18:43,066
people of understanding,  of wisdom and of strength,

202
00:18:43,092 --> 00:18:47,212
that “Whatever may come I will stand by it,

203
00:18:47,236 --> 00:18:53,770
I will take to it, I’ll cope with it,
I’ll change myself and improve myself“.

204
00:19:06,129 --> 00:19:13,392
So now illusion has been dispelled.
I hope you all have got rid of your illusions.

205
00:19:13,825 --> 00:19:17,880
Also you should have no illusions about yourself.

206
00:19:18,375 --> 00:19:21,691
If you have any illusions you should leave Sahaja Yoga.

207
00:19:21,863 --> 00:19:28,113
But know that you are chosen for this purpose by God’s Will,

208
00:19:28,139 --> 00:19:32,646
that’s why you are here
and you have to take it up, the responsibility

209
00:19:32,871 --> 00:19:37,481
of understanding of this science which is absolute.

210
00:19:37,736 --> 00:19:43,947
And working it out yourself, for yourself as well as for others.

211
00:19:44,596 --> 00:19:48,217
You have felt My love,

212
00:19:48,472 --> 00:19:53,162
but your love must also be felt, because God is love.

213
00:19:53,507 --> 00:19:55,742
So your love must be felt by others.

214
00:19:55,848 --> 00:20:02,594
Other must feel that you are compassionate,
loving, understanding.

215
00:20:02,765 --> 00:20:07,984
That’s all the time this Will of God is flowing through you.

216
00:20:08,294 --> 00:20:11,661
And you have to work it out in such a manner

217
00:20:11,692 --> 00:20:14,581
that people should know that you are a saint,

218
00:20:14,605 --> 00:20:18,412
that this power is flowing through you.

219
00:20:20,562 --> 00:20:23,166
Then the second thing that has happened to you

220
00:20:23,214 --> 00:20:26,885
is that, not the illusion about God and about yourself,

221
00:20:27,247 --> 00:20:32,125
second thing that has happened –
that you have understood the integration,

222
00:20:32,242 --> 00:20:37,655
that in the world there is complete integration which is existing.

223
00:20:40,627 --> 00:20:47,451
Normally if you see the children,
they have their own natural, innate understanding.

224
00:20:47,910 --> 00:20:51,564
They know. If you see, normally, a good child

225
00:20:51,644 --> 00:20:54,898
would always like to share his things,

226
00:20:55,218 --> 00:20:57,955
would like to love another child,

227
00:20:58,053 --> 00:21:02,090
if there’s another little child is there,
would like to protect that child –

228
00:21:02,188 --> 00:21:09,170
naturally! It won’t think whether it has
black hair or red hair or blue hair.

229
00:21:10,458 --> 00:21:16,085
Naturally, innately a child feels that way.

230
00:21:16,669 --> 00:21:22,313
Also if you take another child, supposing, who is a little baby,

231
00:21:22,937 --> 00:21:30,982
they know that one should be careful about the privacy of the body.

232
00:21:31,426 --> 00:21:35,348
Children don’t want to be made nude before others.

233
00:21:35,418 --> 00:21:39,369
No child likes it. Innately they know.

234
00:21:39,753 --> 00:21:42,739
So all these innate qualities are within you.

235
00:21:43,011 --> 00:21:45,052
Children don’t like to steal anything.

236
00:21:45,100 --> 00:21:48,764
They don’t know what is stealing is.
They have no idea of stealing.

237
00:21:50,833 --> 00:21:57,507
I’ve also seen also children that,
if they go to a place which is very beautiful,

238
00:21:58,017 --> 00:22:03,421
in somebody’s house,
they will always try to keep the beauty of that place.

239
00:22:03,522 --> 00:22:07,461
But if it is already shabby they don’t mind.

240
00:22:09,493 --> 00:22:12,678
So innately all these qualities are there.

241
00:22:12,761 --> 00:22:17,146
I think the countries which are supposed to be
underdeveloped have so many of these

242
00:22:17,294 --> 00:22:22,691
qualities within them, which are innately built within us.

243
00:22:22,847 --> 00:22:25,212
Innocence is innately built.

244
00:22:25,258 --> 00:22:28,269
So the Will of God built up,

245
00:22:28,463 --> 00:22:33,233
first and foremost thing, was innocence, the auspiciousness.

246
00:22:33,363 --> 00:22:37,025
The first thing He did was to create Shri Ganesha,

247
00:22:37,412 --> 00:22:41,552
or I would say, She, because the Will of God is Adi Shakti.

248
00:22:42,230 --> 00:22:48,204
And all this was created first of all to make
the whole world very beautiful.

249
00:22:49,743 --> 00:22:52,666
All these innate qualities were also placed within you.

250
00:22:52,797 --> 00:22:55,168
All those Deities were placed within you.

251
00:22:55,267 --> 00:23:00,966
[They] were specially made, human beings,

252
00:23:01,245 --> 00:23:05,049
that they should become saintly people,

253
00:23:05,110 --> 00:23:09,623
that they should have their saintly, innate sense.

254
00:23:09,718 --> 00:23:12,191
But it happened in the countries which developed,

255
00:23:12,313 --> 00:23:17,453
that our brain was bombarded
by all kinds of television, all kind of things,

256
00:23:17,600 --> 00:23:26,943
and we became very, we can say, we became very vulnerable.

257
00:23:27,651 --> 00:23:33,657
We started getting into the ideas of others.

258
00:23:33,871 --> 00:23:36,978
Anybody who is dominating could dominate us.

259
00:23:37,053 --> 00:23:40,073
It’s not only Hitler who dominated people.

260
00:23:40,372 --> 00:23:46,178
We also see today how much we are dominated,
if you really detach yourself from this world.

261
00:23:46,613 --> 00:23:53,855
For example fashions.
Certain things that come up, people cannot give up at any cost.

262
00:23:54,322 --> 00:24:00,296
They cannot take to something that is sensible
because it’s a fashion.

263
00:24:00,802 --> 00:24:06,010
For example nowadays there’s a fashion,
say to have such a small skirt.

264
00:24:06,211 --> 00:24:08,897
You can’t get a long skirt anywhere.

265
00:24:09,089 --> 00:24:13,016
Everybody has to wear that kind of a skirt

266
00:24:13,264 --> 00:24:18,186
otherwise you are not ‘in’,  you are not in the madhouse!

267
00:24:19,207 --> 00:24:25,114
Now this kind of thing is bombarded on us morning till evening

268
00:24:25,179 --> 00:24:29,598
so, first of all, we become slaves of these entrepreneurs.

269
00:24:30,475 --> 00:24:34,171
Whatever they give us now, I was told that in Belgium
you cannot get anything fresh.

270
00:24:34,285 --> 00:24:39,505
You have to take everything from the supermarket,
which is all tinned.

271
00:24:40,021 --> 00:24:45,638
Gradually what is happening to us –
we are getting absolutely artificial.

272
00:24:45,877 --> 00:24:49,538
The food is artificial, the dress is artificial,

273
00:24:49,578 --> 00:24:52,309
our whole attitude becomes artificial

274
00:24:52,436 --> 00:24:55,937
because we are so much bombarded by advertisement,

275
00:24:55,993 --> 00:24:59,613
by all kinds of outside influences

276
00:24:59,713 --> 00:25:01,516
that we just get lost

277
00:25:01,630 --> 00:25:04,767
and we forget what is our innate sense

278
00:25:04,802 --> 00:25:09,358
which is being dominated by all these modern things.

279
00:25:09,790 --> 00:25:13,728
So adding up to the science also

280
00:25:13,815 --> 00:25:20,398
there is  a big progress in another direction,  that we can call,

281
00:25:20,702 --> 00:25:24,072
the money became very important.

282
00:25:24,279 --> 00:25:26,330
Once money becomes important,

283
00:25:26,420 --> 00:25:30,275
then all your entrepreneurs become important,

284
00:25:30,341 --> 00:25:33,422
because they know how to make money and befool you all the time.

285
00:25:33,470 --> 00:25:35,903
Today you have this thing, tomorrow you have that thing.

286
00:25:35,928 --> 00:25:38,426
Today you change this and have this thing.

287
00:25:39,449 --> 00:25:43,750
But those people who are innately built, they do not change!

288
00:25:44,802 --> 00:25:49,105
They have their dresses of the same type, they do not change.

289
00:25:49,456 --> 00:25:53,416
On the contrary they find it very difficult to get out of

290
00:25:53,517 --> 00:25:57,693
their traditional achievements and they don’t want to change themselves.

291
00:25:57,959 --> 00:26:01,175
So for sahaja yogis it is important to see and watch

292
00:26:01,261 --> 00:26:06,960
if they are getting this slavery from
the entrepreneurs in modern times.

293
00:26:07,410 --> 00:26:14,905
Then, the thoughts.
So many books we read, which gives you thoughts,

294
00:26:15,158 --> 00:26:22,661
which are some mad rambling,
I would say, of some madman, like Freud.

295
00:26:23,066 --> 00:26:25,710
How could Freud influence the West?

296
00:26:25,877 --> 00:26:32,015
Because you have lost your innate sense and you accepted.

297
00:26:34,073 --> 00:26:41,859
You accepted that and that’s how Freud became your,
sort of a, Jesus Christ.

298
00:26:42,420 --> 00:26:45,128
He became the most important thing.

299
00:26:45,183 --> 00:26:52,648
Sex became the most important thing. I mean it’s so simple.

300
00:26:52,745 --> 00:26:55,603
With little common sense you can understand

301
00:26:55,731 --> 00:27:02,701
that, at every moment, we are put into this kind of a

302
00:27:09,246 --> 00:27:14,975
of a domination by these few

303
00:27:15,168 --> 00:27:19,677
domineering people who have certain ideas,
and they put forward.

304
00:27:20,020 --> 00:27:25,389
Anybody puts any idea. For example,
Sade (the Marquis de Sade) or Sartre or anyone.

305
00:27:25,813 --> 00:27:29,855
That idea starts becoming “Oh he said it“.
Who is he?

306
00:27:29,932 --> 00:27:34,309
What is his life?
Just see for yourself what sort of a man he is.

307
00:27:34,365 --> 00:27:38,368
With little common sense.
But with your will that you have now,

308
00:27:38,612 --> 00:27:42,572
Will of God, which has fashioned the whole world,
which has fashioned you.

309
00:27:42,596 --> 00:27:47,898
Every cell within you has been fashioned by God Almighty

310
00:27:48,022 --> 00:27:53,282
and what you are doing is to play
into the hands of these entrepreneurs.

311
00:27:53,687 --> 00:28:00,907
They have realised that these vulnerable people are very good for

312
00:28:01,329 --> 00:28:11,480
having as their disciples,  I should say,
to make money, to befool them.

313
00:28:11,970 --> 00:28:17,325
Now on this side, you have such a Great Power,

314
00:28:18,371 --> 00:28:21,174
you are chosen for a, such a great thing,

315
00:28:21,280 --> 00:28:26,908
and on the other side you have this kind of slavery.

316
00:28:29,723 --> 00:28:34,191
So try to understand that your innate qualities were lost.

317
00:28:34,308 --> 00:28:39,483
But luckily, by the Kundalini awakening
and by the breaking of the Sahastrara,

318
00:28:39,616 --> 00:28:43,920
all these innate qualities which looked like lost:

319
00:28:43,970 --> 00:28:47,315
like your innocence, like your creativity,

320
00:28:47,526 --> 00:28:54,429
like your religion within, like your compassion

321
00:28:55,200 --> 00:29:05,247
and love for the humanity ,
like your power of judgment, wisdom.

322
00:29:05,555 --> 00:29:10,179
All these great qualities which we thought were lost were nothing

323
00:29:10,306 --> 00:29:13,834
but they were in a dormant state.

324
00:29:13,974 --> 00:29:16,945
They all got awakened one by one.

325
00:29:16,994 --> 00:29:19,812
I don’t have to tell you “Don’t drink this!

326
00:29:19,968 --> 00:29:22,768
Don’t eat this! Don’t do that!”.

327
00:29:22,838 --> 00:29:27,020
You yourself realise that this is wrong.

328
00:29:27,533 --> 00:29:30,668
You yourself know what is good for you.

329
00:29:30,763 --> 00:29:34,139
And still if you want to do wrong you can go ahead.

330
00:29:34,674 --> 00:29:38,821
But already there is a light within you to see for yourself

331
00:29:38,893 --> 00:29:40,868
what is good and what is bad.

332
00:29:40,893 --> 00:29:45,328
It has come because of this Sahastrara being opened out

333
00:29:45,362 --> 00:29:48,286
to this – a new dimension of new knowledge.

334
00:29:48,352 --> 00:29:51,497
And this is not new, it is all innately built within you.

335
00:29:51,520 --> 00:29:57,388
Now all those innate qualities are manifesting
and you are enjoying them.

336
00:29:59,662 --> 00:30:04,182
So now you have to get out of your petty ideas and petty things.

337
00:30:04,923 --> 00:30:07,615
People are reporting to Me something very funny –

338
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:09,854
I can’t believe sahaja yogis can do like that –

339
00:30:09,878 --> 00:30:12,869
that they run away with the plates that I have bought,

340
00:30:12,916 --> 00:30:16,487
or they run away with the cups, they throw things here and there,

341
00:30:16,557 --> 00:30:18,863
all over the places they are throwing things.

342
00:30:18,936 --> 00:30:21,486
How can you behave like this?

343
00:30:22,564 --> 00:30:26,091
I mean this is so stupid and so insipid.

344
00:30:26,204 --> 00:30:30,471
If you do not have a proper discipline of life yourself,

345
00:30:30,608 --> 00:30:34,100
you cannot carry the Will of God, you cannot.

346
00:30:34,170 --> 00:30:38,681
But I’m not going to tell you “Do this or do that!”

347
00:30:38,804 --> 00:30:41,586
I respect your freedom

348
00:30:42,584 --> 00:30:48,616
and I just want that your own Kundalini should awaken
that wisdom in you,

349
00:30:48,784 --> 00:30:51,905
that greatness in you, that glory in you

350
00:30:51,992 --> 00:30:56,317
and you start understanding what is our innate quality.

351
00:30:57,394 --> 00:30:59,432
So it will purify you.

352
00:30:59,539 --> 00:31:01,898
Once you are purified completely, like

353
00:31:01,961 --> 00:31:04,615
you see, if you have some gold which is not pure

354
00:31:04,646 --> 00:31:09,741
you put it in the fire,  the gold is separated.

355
00:31:09,768 --> 00:31:14,937
In the same way, the fire of Kundalini cleanses you completely,

356
00:31:15,039 --> 00:31:17,570
makes you absolutely clean,

357
00:31:17,618 --> 00:31:24,707
and you start seeing your own glory,
your own nature, your own greatness.

358
00:31:24,876 --> 00:31:30,375
So the integration part comes to you easily.
You start integrating.

359
00:31:30,973 --> 00:31:39,379
First of all, we used to have sahaja yogis, say from,

360
00:31:39,436 --> 00:31:44,193
some from England, some from Spain, some from here.

361
00:31:44,205 --> 00:31:48,034
They would always have different groups,
they would never sit together.

362
00:31:48,242 --> 00:31:50,689
You could make out this is English sitting here,

363
00:31:50,781 --> 00:31:55,804
they are sitting here, they are sitting here,
and they would form a group.

364
00:31:56,103 --> 00:32:04,247
But now it’s not so. Now I find they all are becoming integrated.

365
00:32:04,565 --> 00:32:12,330
The integration of human beings is
the most important thing for Sahaja Yoga.

366
00:32:13,469 --> 00:32:18,189
That comes by understanding, not by your intelligence,

367
00:32:18,301 --> 00:32:23,975
but by innate understanding that –
all human beings are made by God,

368
00:32:24,070 --> 00:32:29,339
by His will, and we have no right to despise anyone.

369
00:32:30,191 --> 00:32:36,093
The second integration that has come within you is that all religions,

370
00:32:36,482 --> 00:32:44,225
all religions, are born on the same tree of spiritual life.

371
00:32:46,524 --> 00:32:54,265
That all religions are to be worshipped, all incarnations,

372
00:32:54,388 --> 00:33:00,782
all prophets, all scriptures are to be worshipped.

373
00:33:00,901 --> 00:33:05,408
There are defects, there are problems with
those scriptures which can be corrected.

374
00:33:05,953 --> 00:33:11,078
So gradually you start entering into the subtler side of Divinity,

375
00:33:11,157 --> 00:33:15,479
to understand that all these people have worked hard

376
00:33:15,616 --> 00:33:18,696
to create, today, the atmosphere for Sahaja Yoga,

377
00:33:18,786 --> 00:33:24,120
and no religion is to be despised,
and no religion is to be attacked,

378
00:33:24,250 --> 00:33:31,239
which is a very, very, absolutely a unreal thing

379
00:33:31,410 --> 00:33:37,014
and you are working out a very unreal theory

380
00:33:37,078 --> 00:33:40,658
which doesn’t exist in the Divine plan.

381
00:33:40,764 --> 00:33:44,493
So this is how we finish all fundamentalism.

382
00:33:44,885 --> 00:33:47,837
Fundamentalists are the ones who believed that

383
00:33:47,924 --> 00:33:50,964
this is written in this book, this is written in this book,

384
00:33:51,050 --> 00:33:55,551
and that we, because we read this book, we are something better.

385
00:33:55,664 --> 00:33:59,217
Anybody can read any book, what is so great?

386
00:33:59,647 --> 00:34:04,078
Same, I would say, in Sahaja Yoga people
should not become fundamentalist.

387
00:34:04,148 --> 00:34:05,802
Be very careful!

388
00:34:05,957 --> 00:34:08,592
Because that’s what you are – born like that, I mean,

389
00:34:08,711 --> 00:34:11,050
I don’t know, it’s not your innate quality  but

390
00:34:11,124 --> 00:34:14,768
the way you are made that way,
you have fashioned yourself that way,

391
00:34:14,960 --> 00:34:19,261
that you start also making Sahaja Yoga sometimes a fundamental.

392
00:34:19,310 --> 00:34:21,303
“Mother said so.”

393
00:34:21,408 --> 00:34:24,052
Do not use Me anywhere!

394
00:34:24,151 --> 00:34:28,381
“Mother said so!” Is a way you want to dominate others.

395
00:34:29,718 --> 00:34:35,006
You yourself say because now you have a right,
you have an individuality in Sahaja Yoga.

396
00:34:35,186 --> 00:34:38,145
You can say what you have to say yourself,

397
00:34:38,326 --> 00:34:41,342
but don’t say that “Mother has said it!”

398
00:34:41,467 --> 00:34:45,289
Because anybody can start it, like that: “Christ said it!”.

399
00:34:45,389 --> 00:34:51,403
A clergyman or, a say, pope can stand up on his

400
00:34:51,670 --> 00:34:56,746
own platform  and say that Christ has said it.

401
00:34:57,899 --> 00:35:01,459
They can just arbitrarily use all these things.

402
00:35:01,591 --> 00:35:05,516
So nobody has business to use Me arbitrarily.

403
00:35:05,614 --> 00:35:08,021
Whatever you have to say you say yourself.

404
00:35:08,066 --> 00:35:11,484
But don’t ever quote Me as that: “Mother has said it,”

405
00:35:11,580 --> 00:35:15,607
or, “In this book such and such is written,
so this is the line, that is important.

406
00:35:15,700 --> 00:35:20,080
” You are not bound by any line, by whatever I say.

407
00:35:20,145 --> 00:35:25,647
It is you who has to stand up and see for yourself
what you have to say,

408
00:35:25,860 --> 00:35:29,300
because you have to use now your will

409
00:35:30,183 --> 00:35:38,559
and for that you have to develop yourself to have Pure Will,
the Pure Desire of God Almighty.

410
00:35:39,411 --> 00:35:43,928
The integration not only outward, but inward.

411
00:35:44,024 --> 00:35:51,413
Like first of all, whatever we did, our mind used to say one thing,

412
00:35:51,536 --> 00:35:56,362
our heart used to say another thing,
our brain used to say another thing.

413
00:35:56,792 --> 00:36:02,543
Now what has happened that all these 3 things have become one.

414
00:36:02,806 --> 00:36:09,204
So, whatever your brain says is absolutely acceptable to your heart,

415
00:36:09,501 --> 00:36:12,100
absolutely acceptable to your attention.

416
00:36:12,775 --> 00:36:15,844
So you yourself, you have become now integrated.

417
00:36:16,180 --> 00:36:19,264
Many people write “Mother I want to do it, but I can’t do it,”

418
00:36:19,383 --> 00:36:23,260
“Mother it was my desire to do it, but I can’t do it.” Not now.

419
00:36:23,409 --> 00:36:29,879
Now you are completely integrated
and you can easily do the whole thing very well.

420
00:36:30,531 --> 00:36:39,111
If you want to examine yourself,
you should try to find out “Am I integrated or not?

421
00:36:39,303 --> 00:36:42,871
Whatever I’m doing, am I doing with my full heart or not,

422
00:36:42,967 --> 00:36:45,217
with my full attention or not?”

423
00:36:45,314 --> 00:36:50,637
I’ve seen that you do with full heart and full intelligence

424
00:36:50,734 --> 00:36:53,394
but full attention is not there.

425
00:36:53,924 --> 00:36:58,629
Still the attention, which is the first thing
that was enlightened, is not fully used.

426
00:36:58,884 --> 00:37:06,434
So the whole attention should be absolutely there,

427
00:37:06,644 --> 00:37:11,292
that, “I have to do this thing with full attention.”

428
00:37:11,788 --> 00:37:16,574
Otherwise, the integration is not complete, integration is partial.

429
00:37:16,968 --> 00:37:22,363
So these three things have to be completely integrated.

430
00:37:30,190 --> 00:37:34,801
So the integration of all the chakras comes in.

431
00:37:34,886 --> 00:37:38,169
Like whatever you do, has to be auspicious.

432
00:37:38,985 --> 00:37:42,775
Whatever you do has to be with full attention.

433
00:37:43,716 --> 00:37:47,637
Whatever you do has to be absolutely religious.

434
00:37:48,809 --> 00:37:53,833
So like that, all these centres are being absolutely,

435
00:37:53,871 --> 00:37:59,005
one integrated power that you have.

436
00:37:59,226 --> 00:38:01,383
So the whole life should be integrated.

437
00:38:01,436 --> 00:38:04,215
Now, say somebody’s husband is not that level

438
00:38:04,268 --> 00:38:09,140
or somebody’s wife is not of that level,  you shouldn’t bother.

439
00:38:09,308 --> 00:38:15,631
You should just bother about yourself.
Don’t expect anything from anybody else.

440
00:38:15,842 --> 00:38:20,757
It is your duty which is important.
You have to fulfill your duty

441
00:38:20,883 --> 00:38:23,825
and you have to work it out yourself.

442
00:38:23,904 --> 00:38:29,674
Unless and until you understand that it is your individual being

443
00:38:30,133 --> 00:38:34,689
which has achieved it,
and it’s the individual being which has to realise it,

444
00:38:34,809 --> 00:38:40,298
is the individual being that has to become one,
integrated with the rest of them.

445
00:38:40,585 --> 00:38:44,303
If you start putting things, like many a times I’ve seen

446
00:38:44,362 --> 00:38:47,498
[that] if I say something people start thinking

447
00:38:47,550 --> 00:38:51,918
that I am saying for somebody else, they never take it for themselves.

448
00:38:53,488 --> 00:38:58,816
So,not we have to see what is my gain: “I’ve got financial gain" say

449
00:38:58,885 --> 00:39:04,318
“I’ve got physical gains,
I’ve got mental gains, I’ve got joy, happiness”

450
00:39:04,342 --> 00:39:07,448
that’s not the only thing.

451
00:39:09,404 --> 00:39:12,057
That should not be the only criteria.

452
00:39:12,191 --> 00:39:17,815
But what you should have is the understanding

453
00:39:18,478 --> 00:39:25,999
of your own personality which is being specially fashioned

454
00:39:26,193 --> 00:39:33,493
[through] many, many lives for you
to come in this life to get your Realisation,

455
00:39:33,798 --> 00:39:39,197
to do the further work of Will of God.

456
00:39:41,946 --> 00:39:47,201
Every moment when you see a miracle taking place, you do realise

457
00:39:47,278 --> 00:39:49,528
that it’s all done by Paramchaitanya.

458
00:39:49,581 --> 00:39:53,729
But what is Paramchaitanya – is the will of Adi Shakti.

459
00:39:54,074 --> 00:39:57,518
And what is Adi Shakti – is the Will of God.

460
00:39:58,996 --> 00:40:06,985
So, is all, whatever is done, is all ‘fixed entities’,
we can call them,

461
00:40:07,190 --> 00:40:15,393
or these vibrations are like, we can say, DNA tapes.

462
00:40:15,833 --> 00:40:20,309
They all know how they have to fashion you.

463
00:40:20,876 --> 00:40:23,444
See, today it’s very sunny.

464
00:40:23,479 --> 00:40:26,465
Everybody is surprised how can they have.

465
00:40:26,492 --> 00:40:28,835
So many things happen like this.

466
00:40:28,890 --> 00:40:31,987
The other day, we had havan, it was absolutely sunny.

467
00:40:32,201 --> 00:40:34,779
So the whole Cosmos is working for you.

468
00:40:34,865 --> 00:40:38,245
You are on the stage now and you have to see to it,

469
00:40:38,329 --> 00:40:41,569
but if you don’t have faith in yourself,

470
00:40:41,893 --> 00:40:48,498
if you are not confident as to what you are, how can you help?

471
00:40:49,912 --> 00:40:56,601
How can you work out yourself
and work out all the problems of the world,

472
00:40:56,698 --> 00:40:59,046
which are created only by human beings?

473
00:40:59,127 --> 00:41:06,539
So we have to absolutely overthrow all these dominations on us.

474
00:41:06,870 --> 00:41:11,377
First from science. We can prove everything that Sahaja Yoga,

475
00:41:11,442 --> 00:41:15,265
whatever it has said about science, has been proved.

476
00:41:15,465 --> 00:41:21,062
So, we can throw science which is just always,

477
00:41:21,129 --> 00:41:24,358
all the time, in the flux, it’s changing all the time.

478
00:41:24,445 --> 00:41:27,380
Then the so-called religions that we have.

479
00:41:27,476 --> 00:41:32,280
So-called religions because people who have been Catholics,

480
00:41:32,303 --> 00:41:36,525
who have been Protestants, who have been Hindus
or Muslims, or this and that,

481
00:41:36,711 --> 00:41:39,681
they all have got that thing on their heads.

482
00:41:39,877 --> 00:41:42,083
And this has to be thrown away.

483
00:41:42,324 --> 00:41:45,172
We have to become a new personality.

484
00:41:45,368 --> 00:41:50,638
After Realisation, as I said,
you become like a lotuses is from the mud.

485
00:41:52,128 --> 00:41:54,882
So now you have become lotuses and the lotuses

486
00:41:54,908 --> 00:41:58,276
have to throw away all this dead mud,

487
00:41:58,329 --> 00:42:01,400
otherwise fragrance won’t be there.

488
00:42:01,692 --> 00:42:03,554
That, one has to achieve:

489
00:42:03,670 --> 00:42:10,154
is to throw away all these shackles
which are, which are killing you,

490
00:42:16,918 --> 00:42:23,059
which are of no use, but a burden.

491
00:42:23,720 --> 00:42:26,178
And beautiful lotuses as you are

492
00:42:26,313 --> 00:42:31,611
you have to understand that
the whole fashioning has been done so carefully,

493
00:42:31,673 --> 00:42:37,628
with such sweetness, with such delicacy.

494
00:42:39,455 --> 00:42:43,144
So first of all we must have respect for ourselves,

495
00:42:43,586 --> 00:42:47,298
we must have affection and love for others

496
00:42:48,136 --> 00:42:53,723
and we must have respect, means we must have discipline.

497
00:42:54,772 --> 00:42:56,925
We have to have the discipline

498
00:42:57,781 --> 00:43:02,248
because if you respect yourself you’ll definitely discipline yourself

499
00:43:02,379 --> 00:43:04,509
and you’ll make it available.

500
00:43:06,122 --> 00:43:13,152
Now as you can realise, that from My life itself,

501
00:43:13,326 --> 00:43:18,926
that I work very hard, travel a lot,
much more than any one of you can do.

502
00:43:19,085 --> 00:43:26,493
Because I have the will that – I have to bring this world

503
00:43:27,114 --> 00:43:32,636
to that state of enjoyment, to that state of happiness,

504
00:43:32,952 --> 00:43:37,621
to that state of Divinity, where they realise

505
00:43:37,818 --> 00:43:43,512
what is their glory, what is the glory of their Father.

506
00:43:44,166 --> 00:43:47,796
So I work very hard and I never even think

507
00:43:47,892 --> 00:43:49,978
that something will go wrong with Me,

508
00:43:50,029 --> 00:43:52,372
or “This will happen”,  “What will happen?”

509
00:43:52,486 --> 00:43:55,322
I never have bothered you about My family life,

510
00:43:55,400 --> 00:43:58,006
about My children, about anyone.

511
00:43:58,042 --> 00:44:01,739
Whatever problems I had, I am dealing with them Myself.

512
00:44:01,943 --> 00:44:05,153
But here I get such big, big letters from sahaja yogis,

513
00:44:05,377 --> 00:44:10,192
writing about their daughter, their son, this thing, that thing.

514
00:44:10,372 --> 00:44:15,207
Another thing is attachment to family is
the biggest burden on your heads

515
00:44:15,296 --> 00:44:19,167
and all the time you are worried about your children,

516
00:44:19,191 --> 00:44:21,849
you are worried about this, you are worried about that.

517
00:44:21,990 --> 00:44:23,898
That’s not your responsibility.

518
00:44:25,430 --> 00:44:26,984
Please try to understand.

519
00:44:27,200 --> 00:44:30,760
That’s the responsibility of God Almighty.

520
00:44:31,286 --> 00:44:34,332
You can’t do better than Him can you?

521
00:44:34,932 --> 00:44:38,978
But when you try to take the responsibility
He says “All right, look after!”

522
00:44:39,003 --> 00:44:41,161
and the problems start.

523
00:44:43,281 --> 00:44:47,986
‘Detachment’ is the word one should understand in a proper sense.

524
00:44:48,599 --> 00:44:51,213
When I ask people why do you throw things here and there, say

525
00:44:51,236 --> 00:44:53,420
“We are detached!”- wonderful way!

526
00:44:54,610 --> 00:44:57,712
And what about your children? You cling on to them.

527
00:44:58,182 --> 00:45:00,970
What about your own things? You cling on to them.

528
00:45:01,002 --> 00:45:03,905
For a small little thing, they’ll bother My head.

529
00:45:04,297 --> 00:45:08,599
And, when it belongs to Me or to Sahaja Yoga,

530
00:45:08,689 --> 00:45:11,683
then they’ll have a very nice time with it –

531
00:45:11,782 --> 00:45:13,884
and throw it away,  wherever they feel like.

532
00:45:13,908 --> 00:45:16,655
I mean this kind of irresponsibility!

533
00:45:17,445 --> 00:45:20,072
How can you call them divine?

534
00:45:20,497 --> 00:45:22,870
How can they be saintly people?

535
00:45:23,113 --> 00:45:28,704
Saintly people not only are responsible for themselves,
but for everyone.

536
00:45:30,202 --> 00:45:36,622
Very slowly, smoothly, sweetly, with great affection,

537
00:45:36,913 --> 00:45:39,244
I have brought you to this level.

538
00:45:39,637 --> 00:45:42,725
I didn’t ask you to go to Himalayas or stand on your heads

539
00:45:42,815 --> 00:45:46,296
or to donate all your properties to Me.
Nothing of the kind.

540
00:45:47,852 --> 00:45:51,819
We have managed it in a very, very beautiful manner.

541
00:45:52,283 --> 00:45:55,265
Now further, when you have to go further,

542
00:45:56,327 --> 00:46:00,505
then you have to understand that your duties

543
00:46:00,558 --> 00:46:03,582
are to be fulfilled by you and by nobody else.

544
00:46:04,019 --> 00:46:08,746
But these duties are done by you,

545
00:46:08,800 --> 00:46:14,866
are towards your family, towards your house,
towards this, towards that.

546
00:46:16,142 --> 00:46:19,132
No duties towards Sahaja Yoga.

547
00:46:22,830 --> 00:46:27,951
So when you were, before Sahaja Yoga,
you were not attached to anyone,

548
00:46:28,129 --> 00:46:31,465
in the sense – you were only attached to yourself, self-centered.

549
00:46:31,489 --> 00:46:34,104
Now you have widened yourself a little more,

550
00:46:34,128 --> 00:46:37,143
that now you are attached to your wife, to your children.

551
00:46:37,373 --> 00:46:39,956
But that’s just the same.

552
00:46:40,104 --> 00:46:46,048
That is also selfish, because they are your children, you think.

553
00:46:46,187 --> 00:46:51,136
They are not your children, they are the children of God.

554
00:46:51,661 --> 00:46:55,722
I hope all of you are intelligent enough to understand

555
00:46:56,131 --> 00:47:00,724
your responsibility and work it out.

556
00:47:02,049 --> 00:47:05,593
This is a very important thing that has happened to you

557
00:47:05,821 --> 00:47:07,841
that Sahastrara has opened.

558
00:47:07,945 --> 00:47:11,454
Now you can prove the existence of God,

559
00:47:11,493 --> 00:47:15,077
His Will, everything, to the whole world.

560
00:47:15,412 --> 00:47:18,144
Nobody can challenge Sahaja Yoga.

561
00:47:18,199 --> 00:47:21,796
Those scientist who will challenge can be told.

562
00:47:22,054 --> 00:47:26,618
Anybody, whether you’re a scientist, economist, politician, anything,

563
00:47:27,038 --> 00:47:32,203
everything can be explained in the light of Sahaja Yoga

564
00:47:32,316 --> 00:47:36,679
and can be proved that there’s only one politics –that is of God,

565
00:47:36,793 --> 00:47:39,449
one economics – that is of God,

566
00:47:39,498 --> 00:47:45,771
and there is only one religion –
that is of God,  is Vishwa Nirmala Dharma.

567
00:47:46,541 --> 00:47:48,363
It can be proved,

568
00:47:48,734 --> 00:47:53,542
there’s nothing to be afraid of or to worry about.

569
00:47:53,810 --> 00:47:56,410
This all can be proved to the scientist and

570
00:47:56,431 --> 00:48:01,239
to the other intellectuals and to some few people

571
00:48:01,393 --> 00:48:02,598
if they want to listen to us.

572
00:48:02,620 --> 00:48:05,354
If they don’t want to listen to us, forget it.

573
00:48:05,443 --> 00:48:08,435
Because we are so powerful, why should you worry about them?

574
00:48:08,511 --> 00:48:10,747
But, if they are willing to listen to us,

575
00:48:10,796 --> 00:48:16,724
then is better that we tell them
“Now we have discovered this Great Power”,

576
00:48:17,024 --> 00:48:19,532
and if it works out,

577
00:48:19,632 --> 00:48:22,403
if this Great Power works out

578
00:48:22,578 --> 00:48:27,276
then only we can really fashion the whole world in a new way.

579
00:48:27,347 --> 00:48:30,658
I have great hopes from you people,

580
00:48:30,930 --> 00:48:33,509
but the seriousness with which you should take Sahaja Yoga,

581
00:48:33,546 --> 00:48:37,345
for example even meditation, people don’t do.

582
00:48:38,647 --> 00:48:42,499
Simple thing like meditation,
you people don’t do,  I can’t understand.

583
00:48:42,588 --> 00:48:45,006
How will you grow without meditation?

584
00:48:45,528 --> 00:48:51,178
Unless and until you become thoughtlessly aware you cannot grow.

585
00:48:51,423 --> 00:48:56,398
So you have to, you have to at least meditate morning, evening.

586
00:48:56,536 --> 00:49:00,496
There are many people who are not even collective by temperament.

587
00:49:00,555 --> 00:49:04,707
If they are staying in an ashram
they just think that ashram life is no good.

588
00:49:04,733 --> 00:49:07,720
Such people should really get out of Sahaja Yoga,

589
00:49:08,565 --> 00:49:11,892
because they have not yet understood what this Sahaja Yoga is.

590
00:49:12,175 --> 00:49:14,596
Without collectivity how will you grow?

591
00:49:15,237 --> 00:49:17,291
How will you assemble your power? You see?

592
00:49:17,396 --> 00:49:21,803
You know very well that in a sangha, in a group,

593
00:49:21,976 --> 00:49:26,452
in combining together only, you can be strong.

594
00:49:26,715 --> 00:49:30,214
Is a fact that if you have one stick you can break it,

595
00:49:30,268 --> 00:49:33,775
but if you put many sticks together you cannot break it.

596
00:49:33,892 --> 00:49:38,489
But there are still people
I know who are still not so much in collectivity.

597
00:49:38,679 --> 00:49:43,142
Shows how poor they are in their understanding of their own Self,

598
00:49:43,304 --> 00:49:44,967
and they are telling Me that “Mother,

599
00:49:44,998 --> 00:49:49,182
we don’t want to stay in the Ashram  now anywhere more.”

600
00:49:49,252 --> 00:49:51,982
So they should get out of Sahaja Yoga.

601
00:49:53,159 --> 00:49:55,735
Without the collectivity, you cannot grow.

602
00:49:55,752 --> 00:49:59,319
Without the discipline of Sahaja Yoga, you cannot grow.

603
00:49:59,696 --> 00:50:04,713
It’s better to have ten people of good quality
than to have thousand useless people.

604
00:50:05,302 --> 00:50:07,362
That’s what is the Will of God.

605
00:50:07,545 --> 00:50:11,468
So now, as you are today here,  so many people,

606
00:50:11,501 --> 00:50:15,183
I am really enamoured  to see so many people are there.

607
00:50:15,431 --> 00:50:20,369
And we have done so much of our growth

608
00:50:20,395 --> 00:50:25,017
and grown out of all those
nonsensical things that we were following.

609
00:50:25,459 --> 00:50:29,351
But today we have to take a vow

610
00:50:29,667 --> 00:50:35,205
that –  “I’ll now fashion my life according to the Will of God.

611
00:50:35,234 --> 00:50:38,786
Absolutely. And dedicate myself to that.”

612
00:50:38,815 --> 00:50:43,369
No family, no other considerations.

613
00:50:43,406 --> 00:50:46,809
Just forget it! Nothing so important.

614
00:50:47,154 --> 00:50:50,503
Everything can be looked after by Will of God.

615
00:50:50,739 --> 00:50:54,020
So if you just try to follow the Will of God,

616
00:50:54,052 --> 00:50:56,293
your children will be looked after,

617
00:50:56,316 --> 00:51:00,651
everything will be looked after,
you don’t have to worry for anything.

618
00:51:01,102 --> 00:51:02,533
And that works.

619
00:51:02,619 --> 00:51:05,977
Just try to understand that you have problems

620
00:51:06,002 --> 00:51:08,936
because you don’t want to give those problems to God,

621
00:51:08,961 --> 00:51:11,737
you want to keep it to themselves, that’s why you have problems.

622
00:51:11,793 --> 00:51:13,833
If you decide that “No,

623
00:51:14,269 --> 00:51:19,729
I just want to give these problems to the God’s will,” Finished!

624
00:51:20,842 --> 00:51:25,462
Also there are some who want to say that “We are not so capable

625
00:51:25,544 --> 00:51:30,998
Mother, we can’t do it.”
Saying like this also is stupid.

626
00:51:32,638 --> 00:51:36,661
You test yourself, you see for yourself.

627
00:51:37,534 --> 00:51:41,604
So first of all, one has to understand why do we say such a thing?

628
00:51:42,167 --> 00:51:45,238
Maybe that we are very money-oriented,

629
00:51:45,444 --> 00:51:49,444
that we want to have money to ourselves, or something like that.

630
00:51:49,650 --> 00:51:53,805
Or some people are there who talk of business also in Sahaja Yoga.

631
00:51:54,076 --> 00:51:57,448
There must be something like a money orientation,

632
00:51:57,612 --> 00:52:00,021
or some sort of a material attachment

633
00:52:00,069 --> 00:52:04,091
that they say that ‘We are not capable,
we cannot change.”

634
00:52:04,535 --> 00:52:08,302
The second could be this mamatwa as they call it.

635
00:52:08,350 --> 00:52:13,333
The attachment to your family, children, this, that.

636
00:52:13,765 --> 00:52:16,322
Or, ‘This is mine, this is mine,this is mine.”

637
00:52:16,590 --> 00:52:18,898
This could be the second reason

638
00:52:19,034 --> 00:52:22,735
that you think that you are not bold enough

639
00:52:22,759 --> 00:52:27,008
or you are not strong enough to do Sahaja Yoga.

640
00:52:27,180 --> 00:52:32,851
Thirdly could be that you are still playing with your old habits

641
00:52:33,312 --> 00:52:38,486
and that you are enjoying your life without virtues.

642
00:52:39,530 --> 00:52:41,971
There can be some reason like that.

643
00:52:42,034 --> 00:52:46,381
So just try to locate, “Why am I behaving like this?

644
00:52:46,500 --> 00:52:51,519
Why am I not getting into the same

645
00:52:51,615 --> 00:52:58,358
beautiful path of my ascent as everybody has got it.”

646
00:52:59,000 --> 00:53:03,508
If we introspect, you’ll find out that
"There’s something wrong with me

647
00:53:03,930 --> 00:53:06,711
that I think I am not capable of doing.”

648
00:53:06,802 --> 00:53:09,788
You are capable of doing everything!

649
00:53:10,216 --> 00:53:13,110
You just try this and enjoy it.

650
00:53:14,135 --> 00:53:20,822
So, most important thing now [that]
remains is that you should become a

651
00:53:21,845 --> 00:53:27,798
proper, strong, compassionate vehicle of God’s Will.

652
00:53:28,431 --> 00:53:32,968
So. Then, what is most important of course,

653
00:53:33,004 --> 00:53:37,552
I agree, that you do My puja,
because that helps you a lot, no doubt.

654
00:53:37,578 --> 00:53:40,536
But other things are not important.

655
00:53:42,943 --> 00:53:47,302
So many other things you people tell Me is not of importance.

656
00:53:48,362 --> 00:53:53,461
Main thing is that you should all ascend higher and higher

657
00:53:53,999 --> 00:53:59,763
and compete with each other in getting into higher situation.

658
00:54:00,328 --> 00:54:06,165
As it is, I think in such a short time
we have achieved a lot, no doubt,

659
00:54:06,247 --> 00:54:10,227
but still we have to speed up and work it out.

660
00:54:10,445 --> 00:54:15,835
I am sure that this new science,
or we can say, the, which is the

661
00:54:16,443 --> 00:54:20,241
absolute science will one day outshadow

662
00:54:20,376 --> 00:54:23,791
the other science, and tell people that: this is what it is.

663
00:54:23,813 --> 00:54:26,363
It is in your hands, you work it out.

664
00:54:27,101 --> 00:54:30,768
So today is the day we are celebrate by which

665
00:54:30,818 --> 00:54:35,451
we have opened absolutely a new dimension,

666
00:54:37,340 --> 00:54:45,381
absolutely a venue of great Divinity,

667
00:54:45,539 --> 00:54:49,076
of the proofs of Divine.

668
00:54:49,154 --> 00:54:58,218
And this is something so great that we can really finish

669
00:54:58,242 --> 00:55:03,639
all the illusions they have about themselves, about their ego.

670
00:55:03,769 --> 00:55:05,659
We can manage them.

671
00:55:05,741 --> 00:55:08,938
That power you all have.

672
00:55:10,262 --> 00:55:15,355
May God bless you all.

